<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Meeting Invitation</title>
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }
    h2 {
      color: #333;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #555;
    }
    .meeting-details {
      margin: 20px 0;
      padding: 15px;
      background-color: #f0f4f8;
      border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .join-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #3b82f6;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .footer {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #aaa;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>You’re Invited to a Meeting</h2>
    <p>Hello [User],</p>
    <p>You have been invited to a meeting. Please find the details below:</p>

    <div class="meeting-details">
      <strong>Topic:</strong> Project Kickoff Meeting<br>
      <strong>Date:</strong> Tuesday, May 14, 2025<br>
      <strong>Time:</strong> 10:00 AM – 11:00 AM (UTC)<br>
      <strong>Host:</strong> John Smith
    </div>

    <p>To join the meeting, click the button below:</p>

    <a class="join-button" href="https://example.com/join/meeting-id-12345" target="_blank">
      Join Meeting
    </a>

    <p>If the button above doesn’t work, copy and paste this link into your browser:<br>
      <a href="https://example.com/join/meeting-id-12345">https://example.com/join/meeting-id-12345</a>
    </p>

    <p>Looking forward to seeing you there!</p>

    <p>Best regards,<br>Your Company Team</p>

    <div class="footer">
      &copy; 2025 Your Company. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
